                    "description": "In tandem with my research functions, I am involved in many teaching activities, especially as a design and research coach. I coach at the bachelor and master level. \n\u2022 Strategic Product Design Research Project (TU Delft)  2010~2015 (Master level). During this period, I have coached 6 pairs of students every year. \n\u2022 Bachelor End Project (TU Delft)  2013~2015 (Bachelor level). During this period, I coached 10 to 20 individual students every year.\n\u2022 Design Theory and Methodology (TU Delft)  2012 and 2015 (Master level). In this course, I coached 22 triads of students and occasionally lectured to the 200 student of whole course.\n\u2022 PO3 Fuzzy Front End (TU Delft)  2010(Bachelor level). In this course, I coached 2 groups of 5 students.\n\u2022 Mentor of 4 Master graduation students (TU Delft)   2012~2015\n\u2022 Invited lecture in Expressive Innovations & Design (Aalto University)  December 2013",
