                    "description": "In my PhD research, I am investigating the influence of external stimuli on the creative work of designers. My research fits into the field of design methodology, creativity, cognition and creative problem solving. The focus of my research is on the outcome and cognitive processes of designers, in order to understand how do designers come across and are influenced by possible inspiration sources in the creation of their ideas. In order to do this, I am employing a combination of quantitative and qualitative research methods, to better capture the inspiration process of designers. \nMy goal is to support designers to better understand and implement the most effective practices of inspiration search, in order to promote creativity and innovation.",
